00:32:10.120 --> 00:32:12.390 align:middle line:84%
Power, safety.
Anything else?

00:32:12.390 --> 00:32:15.055 align:middle line:84%
Or that feel like that names it?
That names it.

00:32:15.055 --> 00:32:16.780 align:middle line:84%
I think that's a
