00:32:19.930 --> 00:32:24.280 align:middle line:84%
But just getting to naming it
explicitly of not just what

00:32:24.280 --> 00:32:26.460 align:middle line:84%
I think they're doing,
being against me

00:32:26.460 --> 00:32:29.100 align:middle line:84%
