00:33:33.763 --> 00:33:34.980 align:middle line:90%
Mmhmm.

00:33:34.980 --> 00:33:39.280 align:middle line:90%
So I consider that as well.

00:33:39.280 --> 00:33:40.360 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:33:40.360 --> 00:33:42.570 align:middle line:84%
And for me part of the practice,
