00:33:42.570 --> 00:33:46.770 align:middle line:84%
is can I name-- can I get
connected to what is it when

00:33:46.770 --> 00:33:48.390 align:middle line:90%
I'm having this reaction?

00:33:48.390 --> 00:33:50.340 align:middle line:84%
Because I like
your idea of going

00:33:50.340 --> 00:33:53.390 align:middle line:84%
to some positive image that
